# tommy boilerplate

## 使用技術
- Vue3
- TypeScript
- Vite
- Pinia
- VueRouter
- Tailwindcss
- Vitest

## Install

```
$ git clone --depth 1 --branch main https://github.com/yuto-tomita/tommy-vue-boilerplate.git your-project-name
$ cd your-project-name
$ yarn
```

## Project Start

```
$ yarn dev
```
